Discover The Scent 




Creating Basil & Neroli 







X

Tasting Notes

  A fresh, sophisticated, sensual floral with green facets - stunning in its simplicity.  

– Anne Flipo, Master Perfumer






Top Note: Basil Grande Vert
Top Note: Basil Grande Vert
The herbaceous warmth of basil, with a peppery edge, adds an unexpected twist to the vibrant citrus notes.
 







Heart Note: Neroli
Heart Note: Neroli
The hand-picked blossoms of the bitter orange tree. Neroli is a green floral note, wonderfully clean and fresh.It infuses the fragrance with the elegant scent of orange flower.
 







Base Note: White Musk
Base Note: White Musk
Powdery and clean, it enhances the trail of the scent, adding a softness that endures.
 























   








